mainHeaderLabel.message: Official apps from the team at Unsplash

mainHeader.message: Bringing you thousands of magical moments to your screens

iOSBody.message: Unsplash for iOS is super focused on doing just one thing well: getting great images into creative applications quickly and easily.

ratings.description: {n} here will already be formatted using suffixes notations, such as 'K', 'M', etc

wallpaperHeadingLabel.message: A breathtaking photo for your desktop wallpaper, every day

wallpaperBody.message: From space pics taken by NASA, to bewitching urban streetscapes, to astounding shots of nature taken by high-flying drones—find mesmerizing wallpaper for your Mac in seconds.

instantHeadingLabel.message: Beautiful photos from Unsplash in your new tabs

instantBody.message: Each time you open a new tab, Unsplash Instant will show you a beautiful high-resolution photo from Unsplash — free to download and use however you want.

tvHeadingLabel.message: Beautiful photos from Unsplash on your Apple TV

tvBody.message: Unsplash for Apple TV is a simple slideshow that displays new high-resolution photos from the Unsplash community every 30 seconds, fullscreen on your TV.

unsplashApiBody.message: It’s never been easier to make something awesome with Unsplash photos.

wordpressBody.message: Search for the perfect image for your content from Unsplash directly from your WordPress editor.

figmaBody.message: Bringing over 3 million images from Unsplash right into Figma.

chromeBody.message: This official Unsplash for Chrome extension enables you to quickly search and insert beautiful photos into any web page.

iOSPhotoPickerBody.message: UnsplashPhotoPicker is an iOS UI component that allows you to quickly search the Unsplash library for free high-quality photos with just a few lines of code.

androidPhotoPickerBody.message: UnsplashPhotoPicker is an Android UI component that allows you to quickly search the Unsplash library for free high-quality photos with just a few lines of code.
